<node id="ScaleHLS">
  <data key="d0">ScaleHLS</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">ScaleHLS performs high-level optimizations in MLIR and generates annotated C/C++ code for Vivado HLS.&lt;SEP&gt;ScaleHLS is a tool that performs high-level optimizations in MLIR and generates annotated C/C++ code for Vivado HLS, but it does not deal with hardware/software partitioning or system-level concerns.&lt;SEP&gt;ScaleHLS is an HLS tool used for FPGA or ASIC synthesis and is compared against SODA-OPT.&lt;SEP&gt;ScaleHLS is a new scalable high-level synthesis framework based on multi-level intermediate representation, as described in the paper by Ye et al.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1dc4a868072141c957b2a260dbd14959&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-434fe16e9313a890ebca0145e7c4f4e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8993318ac130965c4393ca23d77a9b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46785dd71a0753269bf4434c15eff5ce</data>
