  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Hot &amp; Spicy translates annotated Python into an accelerator and its runtime Python wrappers.&lt;SEP&gt;Hot &amp; Spicy is a tool that translates annotated Python into SDSoC implementations, focusing on specific optimizations for hardware synthesis.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1dc4a868072141c957b2a260dbd14959&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-434fe16e9313a890ebca0145e7c4f4e7</data>
