  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">HPVM2FPGA synthesizes efficient RTL descriptions for FPGAs by leveraging HeteroC++ and HPVM.&lt;SEP&gt;HPVM2FPGA is a tool that translates HeteroC++ into FPGA implementations, focusing on specific optimizations for hardware synthesis.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1dc4a868072141c957b2a260dbd14959&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-434fe16e9313a890ebca0145e7c4f4e7</data>
