  <data key="d0">Phism</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Phism proposes to exploit MLIR to bridge the gap between polyhedral tools and HLS, aiming to support Vitis HLS through its LLVM frontend.&lt;SEP&gt;Phism is a tool that translates C/C++ into Vitis HLS implementations, focusing on specific optimizations for hardware synthesis.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1dc4a868072141c957b2a260dbd14959&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-434fe16e9313a890ebca0145e7c4f4e7</data>
