<node id="ASIC">
  <data key="d0">ASIC</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">ASIC stands for Application-Specific Integrated Circuit, another hardware target for SODA-OPT's accelerators.&lt;SEP&gt;ASIC is an abbreviation for Application-Specific Integrated Circuit, designed and manufactured for specific purposes.</data>
