<node id="ML-CGRA">
  <data key="d0">ML-CGRA</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">ML-CGRA is an integrated compilation framework designed for efficient machine learning acceleration on CGRAs.&lt;SEP&gt;ML-CGRA is an open-source integrated compilation framework for efficient machine learning implementation and acceleration on CGRAs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d3b54ca06794c60a35a49b96c496c299&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46c9950a6d7f273199820d455082eed4</data>
