  <data key="d0">Coarse-Grained Reconfigurable Arrays (CGRAs)</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">CGRAs are flexible hardware devices with the potential for better power and energy efficiency, but current compilation frameworks focus on inner-most loop kernel acceleration through low-level instruction-based approaches.</data>
