</node>
<node id="CGRAs">
  <data key="d0">CGRAs</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">CGRAs are spatial accelerators optimized for specific ML operations and can be pre-configured as systolic arrays or optimal spatial accelerators.&lt;SEP&gt;CGRAs (Configurable Gate Arrays) are used in the mapping and execution of operations in the VecPAC architecture.&lt;SEP&gt;Coarse-grained Reconfigurable Arrays (CGRAs) are hardware accelerators that provide flexibility and efficiency in processing data streams.&lt;SEP&gt;CGRAs are reconfigurable architectures designed for complex data processing pipelines.&lt;SEP&gt;CGRAs are computational resources that can be reconfigured dynamically based on input data size.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-53afaaa50e93cade10b3194ac28eed31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d3b54ca06794c60a35a49b96c496c299&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72c65d5d8186bf9226fd5144f638e4f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92e82cee01030c7760843fcd3f03ed32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ece4f507673e067d1b26b4c5db6aaef9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21d2d2feb71f0873f5e6a7016d1a0185&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80f80a02f12f4e7d9000fea69ce18385&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57a3a682d8c8b22c568166b68710bb5e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1766410720</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Systolic Array Configuration">
  <data key="d0">Systolic Array Configuration</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The CGRA can be configured as a systolic array for matrix multiplication.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-53afaaa50e93cade10b3194ac28eed31</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1766322486</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
