  <data key="d0">Vector Functional Unit (FU)</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A vector functional unit is part of the CGRA architecture designed for vector operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-867038b972ebe25908221a61e9ba9a9c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1766322520</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Scalar Functional Unit (FU)">
  <data key="d0">Scalar Functional Unit (FU)</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A scalar functional unit is a component in the tile architecture that handles scalar operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-867038b972ebe25908221a61e9ba9a9c</data>
