  <data key="d0">Speedup</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Speedup measures the performance improvement of one execution over another, often in terms of time or resources.&lt;SEP&gt;Speedup indicates how much faster VecPAC performs compared to the scalar CGRA baseline, normalized for comparison.</data>
