  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Accuracy describes how closely the computed results match the expected values.&lt;SEP&gt;Accuracy represents the level of correctness achieved by VecPAC in different application domains.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ece4f507673e067d1b26b4c5db6aaef9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e2dc42cf9d2604980f8a4ea00b9e5e9</data>
