  <data key="d0">HEAL-WEAR</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">HEAL-WEAR is a design template used to enable vector computations for electrocardiogram applications.&lt;SEP&gt;HEAL-WEAR is a vector CGRA designed for electrocardiogram (ECG) applications, duplicating the data path in each reconfiguration cell to enable vector computations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb7fb6bd238c27a13ccbffd80022a059&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-709227a765c55f9d3440bf6ca2a72a60</data>
