  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Riken is a CGRA template utilized for exploring the design space of high-performance computing applications.&lt;SEP&gt;Riken is a CGRA template used for HPC applications, allowing each tile to be configured as a SIMD engine with vector lanes.</data>
