<node id="DFG Generation">
  <data key="d0">DFG Generation</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-867038b972ebe25908221a61e9ba9a9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fde1c2f6a78bac431334c31848f80a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f7cad872120e96e22443543d20a47ae</data>
  <data key="d2">VecPAC generates DFGs by representing each basic operation as a node and data dependencies as edges.&lt;SEP&gt;DFG generation and DFG mapping are part of the DRIPS compilation framework.&lt;SEP&gt;DFG generation involves generating a data flow graph from the optimized MLIR description for each kernel.</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1766410738</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
