<node id="DRIPS pipeline rebalancing mechanism">
  <data key="d0">DRIPS pipeline rebalancing mechanism</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The DRIPS pipeline rebalancing mechanism involves identifying kernels with most and least execution cycles and adjusting their resource allocation.</data>
