<node id="DRIPS Architecture">
  <data key="d0">DRIPS Architecture</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">DRIPS architecture is used as the baseline for comparison, featuring a statically partitioned CGRA configuration.&lt;SEP&gt;DRIPS architecture refers to a specific design for CGRA that allows dynamic adjustments and pipelined application execution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2b8e7ceb7ade808ddedfa769ab7b31be&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0663013f37b4f7c3740127aa091def5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c70d15fac8cde95102112baf7572b83a</data>
