<node id="Dataflow Graph">
  <data key="d0">Dataflow Graph</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Dataflow graph (DFG) represents the operations and data dependencies within a loop body of SpMV.&lt;SEP&gt;A dataflow graph remains fixed during execution independently from variations of the input data.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5de0c17cc29f5bae6ae53b83abd67cef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66bbd3d920ec2fc75c516befdf7597d1</data>
