  <data key="d0">Static Hardware Allocation Approach</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">This approach does not allow accelerators to react to input variations, leading to an unbalanced pipeline and reduced throughput.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5de0c17cc29f5bae6ae53b83abd67cef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
