  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">MLIR is the framework used in the development of SODA-OPT.&lt;SEP&gt;SODA-OPT extends MLIR to automate high-level optimizations for hardware accelerator generation.&lt;SEP&gt;SODA-OPT leverages MLIR for defining IRs and performing optimizations.&lt;SEP&gt;SODA-OPT extends the MLIR framework to provide high-level optimizations that are independent of backend tools.&lt;SEP&gt;MLIR is utilized in SODA-OPT for optimization and code partitioning of ML applications.</data>
