  <data key="d8">ML-CGRA integrates compiler optimizations to improve performance while offering a more flexible and end-to-end solution compared to traditional approaches.</data>
  <data key="d9">optimization approach,performance improvement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d3b54ca06794c60a35a49b96c496c299</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1766322499</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="ML-CGRA" target="Instruction Level">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">ML-CGRA avoids operating purely at the instruction level to offer better user flexibility and reduce brittleness compared to traditional approaches.</data>
  <data key="d9">compilation level,user flexibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d3b54ca06794c60a35a49b96c496c299</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1766322499</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="ML-CGRA" target="High-Level Structures in Code">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">ML-CGRA integrates high-level structures in code to enhance performance and provide a more flexible solution on CGRAs.</data>
  <data key="d9">code optimization,performance enhancement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d3b54ca06794c60a35a49b96c496c299</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1766322499</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="ML-CGRA" target="Semantic Information Leverage">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">ML-CGRA utilizes semantic information from ML models for efficient mapping on CGRAs through optimized parametric templates.</data>
  <data key="d9">model optimization,template support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d3b54ca06794c60a35a49b96c496c299</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1766322499</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="ML-CGRA" target="Conventional Compilation Flows">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">ML-CGRA offers a more convenient end-to-end solution compared to traditional compilation flows that require manual refinement and kernel inlining.</data>
