</edge>
<edge source="Cycle-Level Simulation" target="CGRA Runtime Library">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The CGRA runtime library facilitates cycle-level simulation to enable thorough evaluation of performance at a detailed level.&lt;SEP&gt;The CGRA runtime library facilitates cycle-level simulation to evaluate model performance.</data>
  <data key="d9">evaluation,evaluation detail,performance,simulation support</data>
