<edge source="Vector Tiles" target="VecPAC">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Vector tiles are part of the VecPAC architecture to support hybrid and fixed-point operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Applications using VecPAC can leverage vector tiles for higher data parallelism to achieve better performance.</data>
