</edge>
<edge source="VecPAC" target="PyMTL3">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">PyMTL3 models VecPAC to generate synthesizable Verilog code.&lt;SEP&gt;VecPAC is modeled with PyMTL3 to generate Verilog code.</data>
