</edge>
<edge source="VecPAC" target="full32 CGRA">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">VecPAC achieves a performance similar to full32 (1.1× vs 1.15×), but improves area-efficiency by 1.74×.</data>
