</edge>
<edge source="VecPAC" target="Fixed-Point Additions">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">VecPAC supports various fixed-point additions with different bit-width configurations.</data>
  <data key="d9">arithmetic operation,framework support</data>
