</edge>
<edge source="VecPAC" target="64-bit Addition">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The VecPAC framework supports 64-bit additions with carry-bit delivery between appropriate sub-adders.</data>
  <data key="d9">arithmetic operation,framework support</data>
