</edge>
<edge source="VecPAC" target="Loop Vectorization">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">VecPAC supports loop vectorization for improving performance by transforming loop bodies to operate on multiple vector elements in parallel.</data>
  <data key="d9">framework support,optimization technique</data>
