</edge>
<edge source="VecPAC Architecture" target="Area-Efficiency">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hybrid designs like VecPAC are more area-efficient compared to traditional CGRAs with scalar FUs only.</data>
  <data key="d9">resource management,space optimization</data>
