<edge source="ASAP [25]" target="hardware/software co-design framework">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">ASAP is a hardware/software co-design framework that focuses on area-efficient and precision-aware CGRAs but does not support vector computations.</data>
