  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The mapTable is managed and updated by the DRIPS Controller for kernel-tile mappings.&lt;SEP&gt;The DRIPS Controller updates mapTable based on resource allocation status.&lt;SEP&gt;The DRIPS Controller updates mapTable to reflect current state of control signals and mappings.</data>
