<edge source="DRIPS Controller" target="Rebalancing Overhead">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The DRIPS Controller manages kernel rebalancing which impacts overall application performance.&lt;SEP&gt;The DRIPS Controller determines that a kernel needs to be reconﬁgured and triggers the DMA unit to load the corresponding control signals once the kernel completes its current execution.</data>
