</edge>
<edge source="DRIPS Controller" target="Throughput Improvement">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">DRIPS controller dynamically adjusts resource partitioning and rebalancing to improve application throughput.&lt;SEP&gt;The DRIPS Controller dynamically adjusts the size and arrangements of kernels to improve throughput.&lt;SEP&gt;DRIPS controller triggers DMA unit to load control signals for reconfiguring kernels dynamically.</data>
  <data key="d9">dynamic adjustment,reconfiguration</data>
